history.content:
Join us on Wednesday, August 19th at 12:00 pm PST for an information session with Randall Laurence, Optiver's Education Lead, to explore the life-cycle of a trade.

From pricing to execution and evaluation, Randall will speak from over 10 years of Optiver experience and walk you through how math, computer science, engineering and research drive Optiver's business.

Please register in advance for this webinar using this link: https://optiver-us.zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_Co45YkD0R1qyUh4_650ZRg
After registering, you will receive a confirmation email containing information about joining the webinar. We will have a link for students to apply to Optiver's open roles as well!

BONUS: Since we're all spending extra time at home, attendees will be entered to win an Optiver "stay at home" swag pack!
history.subject: Optiver Tech Talk and Resume Drop: August 19 at 12PM!
